txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Tough sword sheaths from intelligent enemies to the north. Deliver the items to Guardsman Otley in the town of Trestlebridge.
'We will be able to refit these for our weapons quickly. Thank you.'
'Part vengeance and part necessity, we need the sword sheaths from the enemies to the north. We need to protect the weapons that we have.'
Men of Bree Task: Tough Sword Sheaths
Guardsman Otley, in Trestlebridge, is awaiting delivery of tough sword sheaths.
Deliver the tough sword sheaths to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge
You have been tasked with collecting tough sword sheaths from intelligent enemies far to the north. You can deliver the items to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge.
Wanted: Tough sword sheaths from intelligent enemies to the north.
